{{Location map|Canada Alberta|lat= 50.523935|long=-110.153324|width=200|caption=Location of Bindloss [[Alberta]]|label=Bindloss}} '''Bindloss''' is a [[hamlet (place)|hamlet]] in [[southern Alberta]] in [[Special Areas Board, Alberta|Special Area No. 2]], located {{convert|10|km}} west of [[Alberta Highway 41|Highway 41]], {{convert|97|km}} north of [[Medicine Hat, Alberta|Medicine Hat]].

